		}
		{
			dependencies: ["9D05"]
			description: [
				"§6Prometheum§r is a unique metal whose armor improves §lpassively§r as you kill enemies while wearing it."
				""
				"The armor starts at modest protection and grows stronger with each kill. It tracks your combat experience permanently, making it the ideal long-term progression armor for an aggressive playstyle."
				""
				"Prometheum ore is found in the overworld at mid-depths. Mine it and smelt it in a blast furnace. The full armor set grows into one of the strongest armor options available."
			]
			icon: "mythicmetals:prometheum_ingot"
			id: "9D08"
