			title: "Prometheum"
			subtitle: "Armor that grows with combat"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -4.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["9D07"]
			description: [
				"§bHallowed§r metal comes from §eHallowed Ore§r found in the Nether. It is brighter and more powerful than Adamantite."
				""
				"Smelt Hallowed Ore in a blast furnace. §6Hallowed Ingots§r are used to craft armor and tools that absorb the radiant energy of the Nether."
				""
				"Hallowed armor provides excellent protection and grants the wearer bonus fire resistance. It is one of the highest-tier metals available before reaching Celestium (End)."
			]
