		{
			dependencies: ["9D09"]
			description: [
				"§6Celestium§r is the ultimate metal in §bMythic Metals§r, found only in the §5End§r dimension as §6End Stone Starrite Ore§r (which yields Celestium)."
				""
				"Smelt it in a blast furnace. §6Celestium Ingots§r produce the highest-stat armor and weapons in the Mythic Metals progression, surpassing Hallowed and Adamantite."
				""
				"Celestium armor provides resistance to all damage types and has innate Knockback resistance. The Celestium Sword is the strongest sword in the Mythic Metals line."
